20 8.1(d)(1)(ii) but are not subsidized by a federal, state, or municipal government subsidy and/or do
21 not have a deed restriction or land lease as described in this subsection (9), shall count as one-half
22 (½) of one unit for the purpose of the calculation of the total of low- or moderate-income year-
